that is shared by our management and people. This respon- sibility extends beyond providing workplaces in accordance with all applicable norms, standards, and requirements. To protect and train our people, we have established the Safety Essentials with core safety behaviors. We expect our people to adhere to those essentials at all times and to place health, safety, and the environment first in all that they do when working for Siemens.

